Reasoning: The paper deals with algorithms for solving parity games, which are a type of game played on directed graphs. This topic falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), as well as computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.GT). The paper also involves complexity analysis and optimization, which could fall under the categories of logic in computer science (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL).
